#  ░▒▓██████▓▒░░▒▓█▓▒░░▒▓█▓▒░░▒▓██████▓▒░░▒▓███████▓▒░   ░▒▓█▓▒░  ░▒▓███████▓▒░       ░▒▓█▓▒░ 
#                                                                                             
#                                                                                             


# Main background, empty for terminal default, need to be empty if you want transparent background
theme[main_bg]=""

# Main text color
theme[main_fg]="#d8c8b4"

# Title color for boxes
theme[title]="#8d623b"

# Highlight color for keyboard shortcuts
theme[hi_fg]="#c19359"

# Background color of selected item in processes box
theme[selected_bg]="#4e3024"

# Foreground color of selected item in processes box
theme[selected_fg]="#d8c8b4"

# Color of inactive/disabled text
theme[inactive_fg]="#4e3024"

# Misc colors for processes box including mini cpu graphs, details memory graph and details status text
theme[proc_misc]="#8f2f2f"



# Cpu box outline color
theme[cpu_box]="#466b61"






# Memory/disks box outline color
theme[mem_box]="#466b61"






# Net up/down box outline color
theme[net_box]="#466b61"






# Processes box outline color
theme[proc_box]="#466b61"






# Box divider line and small boxes line color
theme[div_line]="#4e3024"





# Temperature graph colors
theme[temp_start]="#466b61"
theme[temp_mid]="#c19359"
theme[temp_end]="#b44949"

# CPU graph colors
theme[cpu_start]="#466b61"
theme[cpu_mid]="#c19359"
theme[cpu_end]="#b44949"

# Mem/Disk free meter
theme[free_start]="#5a4432"
theme[free_mid]="#466b61"
theme[free_end]="#61897d"

# Mem/Disk cached meter
theme[cached_start]="#5a4432"
theme[cached_mid]="#ab7f53"
theme[cached_end]="#d2aa73"

# Mem/Disk available meter
theme[available_start]="#5a4432"
theme[available_mid]="#c19359"
theme[available_end]="#d9b67e"

# Mem/Disk used meter
theme[used_start]="#5a4432"
theme[used_mid]="#8f2f2f"
theme[used_end]="#b44949"

# Download graph colors
theme[download_start]="#4e3024"
theme[download_mid]="#ab7f53"
theme[download_end]="#d2aa73"

# Upload graph colors
theme[upload_start]="#4e3024"
theme[upload_mid]="#8f2f2f"
theme[upload_end]="#b44949"

